description: Have you been craving truly authentic Mexican food in the Seattle area? Well, Los Chilangos has got what you've been looking for. This is a taco truck packed to the brim with family recipes, generations of culinary experience, and farmers' market fresh ingredients on the Eastside, and out of the window on the side its dishing out the Mexico City style street food you've unknowingly been waiting for your entire life.With delicious pastor, fantastic carne asada, scrumptious cabeza, and more, this truck is sure to satisfy all Mexican food cravings. Find it in the Seattle area, or bring it to you!
name: Los Chilangos
